{"tid":41655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敘利亞內戰40萬人死亡，受困孩童發「最後訊息」道別世","createTime":"2016-12-16T05:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T06:32:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbb8ecbff5c8f02d1687994e5a7fa05719080a9","tid":41655,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"敘利亞內戰如今邁入第六個年頭，尤其北部城市阿勒頗(Aleppo)東部由叛軍所控制。週二上午，敘利亞總統阿薩德與俄羅斯盟軍發起大規模進攻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/090459_8a75762e8210761c9a216a72acf73c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F090459_8a75762e8210761c9a216a72acf73c08.jpg&h=bbfcb5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在陸空連續猛轟之下，被前線記者形容為「毀滅日」。聯合國與國際社會稱此次軍事行動「泯滅人性」。<br />\n <br />\n數以萬計的阿勒頗平民卡在戰火中動彈不得。當地陸續傳出，反抗區平民遭政府軍士兵集體處決的消息。而網路上也出現戰民透過簡訊、電話與僅存衛星訊號，一一發送「訣別」訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/090536_8c27a032e522b05c724f8308dcbcbf0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F090536_8c27a032e522b05c724f8308dcbcbf0e.jpg&h=af968c63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d3841005089d629ed285ffa33ef646576df807a","tid":41655,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808968155446101f81fb72189d4744033e81a708","tid":41655,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dc273b74327ddf6fc3e7c760a12b99d63ab580","tid":41655,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:17:44.000Z","msg":"link ?"},{"pid":"b061fe1d7936f3daec517f82e71cb494ea6ed26a","tid":41655,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"恭喜